{"type":null,"faqId":23570,"title":"B2手环连接情况下，为何听不到微信语音","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span class=\"s1\">\"B2手环与手机建立连接的情况下，微信语音会从听筒出来，会误以为没有声音。您需要将手机与B2手环断开，这点击收听微信语音时，声音会从扬声器播放。<br>\n或者升级B2固件版本解决，方式如下：下载华为穿戴-&gt;连上B2-&gt;在菜单栏选择更新华为手环，等待更新升级（21.10.07.09.02 及其以上版本）。\"\n<br>\n</span>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7571","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1429866253000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":112,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"B2,连接,微信,语音","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}